    "body": "Yep, but I think it makes sense. The change would only be inside each widget's connector `refine` method, so ~11 files max.\n\nWe could also replace the triple equality check with a deep comparison, which would remain cheap provided we don't have too many complicated states. That shouldn't be a problem with the widgets we have right now.\n",
